metadata.name: Tdub (Trevor Williams)
metadata.description:
this is just a future mint placeholder. but while we've got you here - we may as well tell you a little about the silly looking fella in the photo. this is Tdub also goes by Trevor Williams. he likes cameras. and taking pictures with cameras - lots of them. not only is he funny looking. 
he's also a commercial photographer commissioned by Getty Images, whose photographs are regularly used by major brands and news agencies globally - Apple, Adidas, The New York Times and Microsoft to name a few. we don't know how he managed to do it - but he does take pretty sic photos. take a meta-stroll through his galleries found here - we think you'll agree: 
https://oncyber.io/tdub-forgotten-japan  
https://oncyber.io/fantastical-light

thanks, The Tdub Team
